one time, when i was really really little, it was late, everybody was already in bed, it was thundering and lightening outside, and i thought the thunder was dinosaurs, and they were gonna eat me, so i went and slept under my parents bed, no covers or pillows, i didn't wake them up, i don't even think they know about it..........good story. 

i finally got to work out today, i mean actually get a workout, i don't get to very often now.  

congrats forensics team.

i am not goin to school tomorrow, i actaully don't know if i already typed that, i don't feel like goin back and reading, i know i thought of it before, but eh, whatever. i hope you guys miss me, somebody other than my sweetness whom i love soo much.

my love is so strong for laura, that chuck norris couldn't take it,  well he probably could, but not easily. 

time for bed, even though i took a loong nap before.

i love you guys....EXCEPT YOU, GOD I HATE YOU, FUCK YOU....AHHHH.





so how many of you possibly considered that you were that "YOU".  cause...don't be crazy, i don't hate you, i don't think.

thats a gay reason to like my car, but whatever.

i LOVE how everyone is freaking out. i know it was a very bad thing to do, i feel TERRIBLE about hurting laura and tyler but still. caitlin and i NEVER touched eachother, not one time.  we had chances, we had times when we were completely alone, and could do whatever we wanted, but we DID NOT. but like i said, i know that what we did was bad, but all we did was TALK. come on people relax just a tad. not  that it is anyone else's buisiness but, eh, what can ya do?  People are acting like we did have sex or something. i feel so bad though.....I'M SO SORRY LAURA, and tyler. tyler is pissed at me, he won't even talk to me. i understand and everything, but dayam. anyways...today was the worse day ever...yesterday was awesome, went to tennis practice for the first day, it was cool. i played with coach some, it was awesome. he is like the best guy i have played ever.  he said towards the end of practice "if nothing happens then you will be my top guy" so that means i am gonna be top seed. and jordan will def. be 2nd. thats so awesome. sometimes i think he could beat me...but i would never tell him that...i mean....wait....he reads this doesn't he......damn.....backspace, what?  anyways...i am such a douche....damnit.....i was hoping "it" would go away,and noone find out, so we could just forget about it, cause it was over and i felt good about that, i felt good about bein through with that, still havin not done anything. and ofcourse it blows up in my/our face. welp i guess we asked for it. but i am such a douche, AHHH..damnit, you guys i suck, comment if you agree how bad i suck and for what reasons.
